(Wire format \(compact, current\)) Tj
T*
(Top-level fields:) Tj
T*
(- tx_id) Tj
T*
(- fee \(fixed 9-decimal string; atom-aligned\)) Tj
T*
(- timestamp) Tj
T*
(- inputs) Tj
T*
(- outputs) Tj
T*
(- signature \(witness, canonical base64 on wire\)) Tj
T*
(- pubkey \(witness, canonical base64 on wire\)) Tj
T*
