T*
(- coinbase) Tj
T*
(- metadata \(only when non-empty\)) Tj
T*
(- block_height \(optional metadata field; not consensus payload for fee sizing\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Input fields:) Tj
T*
(- tx_out_id \(<prev_txid>:<vout>\)) Tj
T*
(- script_sig \(canonical SIG_REF:<16hex>\)) Tj
T*
(- sequence \(only included when non-zero\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
