T*
(- input tx_id, index, address duplicates) Tj
T*
(- output tx_out_id payload duplication) Tj
T*
(- tx pubkey_size, signing_hash, signing_hash_mode) Tj
T*
(- always-on default flags/fields that can be derived) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This materially reduced high-input tx size.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(High-input impact:) Tj
T*
(- each extra input now carries only the spend reference \(tx_out_id\) + compact script reference) Tj
T*
(\(SIG_REF\) plus optional non-zero sequence,) Tj
T*
(- no duplicated per-input alias fields are emitted on wire.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
