T*
(- Internal signing/verification still uses Falcon hex values.) Tj
T*
(- Wire format uses canonical base64 for signature and pubkey.) Tj
T*
(- Decoder is strict canonical base64 \(wire_to_hex\(...\)\), with legacy hex disabled by default:) Tj
T*
(- WITNESS_WIRE_ALLOW_HEX_LEGACY = False) Tj
