(- txid: SHA3-384 over no-witness tx \(SegWit-style\).) Tj
T*
(- Signing digest: SHA3-384 over deterministic no-witness signing payload.) Tj
T*
(- wtxid: SHA3-384 over full tx \(with witness\).) Tj
T*
(- Witness never changes txid or signing digest.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Size and weight model) Tj
T*
(Canonical metrics are:) Tj
T*
(- base_bytes) Tj
T*
(- total_bytes) Tj
T*
(- weight = base_bytes * 3 + total_bytes) Tj
T*
(- vsize = ceil\(weight / 4\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Helper: Constants.tx_policy_metrics\(tx\) returns \(base_bytes, total_bytes, weight, vsize\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Policy and consensus sizing both use vsize as the canonical fee/limit unit.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Important:) Tj
T*
(- size_bytes in tx logs is the canonical vsize used for policy.) Tj
T*
(- Raw serialized full bytes are reported separately as total_bytes in diagnostics when needed.) Tj
T*
(- For block packing and fee checks, vsize is the authoritative metric.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Fee policy \(current constants\)) Tj
T*
(- FEE_PER_BYTE_ATOMS = 200) Tj
T*
(- MIN_TRANSACTION_FEE_ATOMS = 187,500 \(0.000187500 ATHO\)) Tj
T*
(- DUST_LIMIT_ATOMS = 5 \(0.000000005 ATHO\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Required fee formula:) Tj
T*
(- required_fee_atoms = max\(vsize * 200, 187500\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(SIG_REF rule \(consistency fix\)) Tj
T*
(script_sig is a compact reference only, never a full embedded signature:) Tj
T*
(- required canonical pattern: SIG_REF:<16hex>) Tj
T*
(- same rule is enforced in send path, mempool validation, tx validation, and block validation) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This removed the prior class of ?accepted in mempool, rejected in block? SIG_REF mismatches.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Bookkeeping field exclusion in policy math) Tj
T*
(Constants.tx_policy_metrics\(...\) strips internal bookkeeping keys before sizing:) Tj
T*
(- block_height) Tj
T*
(- size) Tj
T*
(- size_bytes) Tj
T*
(- size_base_bytes) Tj
T*
(- weight) Tj
T*
(- vsize) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This prevents fee drift when non-consensus metadata is attached during pipeline stages.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Signing flow) Tj
T*
(- Build base tx \(empty witness/signature refs\).) Tj
T*
(- Compute no-witness signing digest.) Tj
T*
(- Sign via Falcon CLI.) Tj
T*
(- Store witness once at tx top-level \(signature, pubkey\).) Tj
T*
